DROP EXTERNAL TABLE F_TransactionsActivities;

CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE F_TransactionsActivities (
	[Posting_Date] date,
	[Line_Total] float,
	[Charge_Weight] numeric(38,2),
	[Linehaul_Booking_ID] int,
	[LMS_Customer] nvarchar(4000),
	[LMSDepotRegion] nvarchar(4000),
	[LMSTransID_Type] nvarchar(4000),
	[LMSTransID] int,
	[SpecDel] int,
	[Movement_Type] nvarchar(4000),
	[System_Account_Code_KEY] nvarchar(4000),
	[Document_Category] nvarchar(4000),
	[Type] nvarchar(4000),
	[Depot] nvarchar(4000),
	[Fleet_Code] nvarchar(4000),
	[Customer_Code_KEY] nvarchar(4000),
	[Depot_Code] nvarchar(4000),
	[TBS_Fleet_Owner] nvarchar(4000),
	[TBS_H_Fleet_Code_Flag] nvarchar(4000),
	[TBS_Local_Load] nvarchar(4000),
	[TBS_Route] nvarchar(4000),
	[TBS_Source] nvarchar(4000)
	)
	WITH (
	LOCATION = 'DataLake/Structured/Facts/T_TransactionsActivities.parquet',
	DATA_SOURCE = [synapse_citylogisticsstorage_dfs_core_windows_net],
	FILE_FORMAT = [SynapseParquetFormat]
	)
GO


SELECT TOP 100 * FROM dbo.F_TransactionsActivities
GO
